# PR: Maringá councilors approve salary and increase in the number of parliamentarians of the municipality - the new democracy

Author: Comitê de Apoio

Description: The Maringá City Council approved, at the end of December of the last year, an increase of 43% in the salaries of the councilors in a plenary of a plenary of

Publish Time: 2023-02-23T16:28:58-03:00

Modified Time: 2023-02-23T16:30:54-03:00

Updated Time: 2023-02-23T16:30:54-03:00

