The reference is to the threats received yesterday by the Minister, on which Digos investigated, appeared four days ago on social media. In particular, you would deal with a post with the written "I dreamed of the barricades in via Bologna tonight. Ela Digos here no longer enters, Valditara upside down". The hint on theBarricate would be a reference to a fact that happened two weeks ago atorino, when it was occupied, by a student collective near the centerosocial Askatasuna, [the Liceoeinstein](https://torino.repubblica.it/cronaca/2023/02/04/news/occupazione_alleinstein_greta_anima_della_protesta_lezioni_da_lunedi_ma_non_siamo_squadristi-386421629/)."Non mi preoccupano le minacce, ritengo si stia creando un brutto clima,occorre abbassare i toni della polemica" dice Valditara. Alzando, in sostanza,i toni. Ed ora la polemica è ancora più infuocata, lo strappo con il mondodella scuola consumato.

