For ** Nicola Fratoianni **, Italian left, the words of Valditara "do not worthy of a minister". And he adds: "Of a liquidator of the schoolpubblica like him our country and the world of school do not know what to do with it". "Scandalous, I express closeness and support to the principal Annalisasavino who underwent an indecent and against lacostonation attack from the minister," he writes in a note ** Angelo Bonelli ** Co-Portavoce of Europe and Green and Left Deputy.

